 &lt;td style="text-align: left">8.6&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">塑料&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">拖鏈，3D列印&lt;a href="https://cad.onshape.com/documents/6626b842adca229e69544ad1/w/89ac2637f82d915f22c2bcd0/e/3a231755273e980d277c3a4c">[CAD]&lt;/a>，輪子，電子設備，管材，電路板&lt;/td>
